{"tid":1102003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維基解密創辦人係英國落網","createTime":"2019-04-11T11:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T06:48:20.000Z","uid":63452,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f132a62d78a2ffa33bbdc0b429077d8bd8d0b1b1","tid":1102003,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"BBC News - Julian Assange: Wikileaks co-founder arrested in London<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-47891737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-47891737&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=69bbaf7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-47891737</a>"},{"pid":"7248da592a9a6509b18f222a953bf1ee84870812","tid":1102003,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:58:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8oqJiNzJQ_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8oqJiNzJQ_E&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=4e5bf47f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8oqJiNzJQ_E</a><br />\nThe Guardian 有片"},{"pid":"3cc6e4f9ed1f7c7bcd2bf93a3dfa6ba89edf6ce2","tid":1102003,"uid":53498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"始終都係避唔到"},{"pid":"dede15fbbce9a663eff25c4e22cc2df018919a07","tid":1102003,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"tldr: Julian Assange 創辦Wikileaks 同年俾瑞典政府全球通緝，指佢2010 年係瑞典強姦左個女人。Julian Assange 指係雙方同意嘅性行為。佢一直匿埋係厄瓜多爾駐英國大使館7 年，直到今日厄瓜多爾唔再保佢，然後俾俾英國政府拉左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-11047811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-11047811&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b5416d1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-11047811</a><br />\n<br />\nHe set up Wikileaks, which publishes confidential documents and images, in 2006, making headlines around the world in April 2010 when it released footage showing US soldiers shooting dead 18 civilians from a helicopter in Iraq.<br />\n<br />\nBut, later that year, he was detained in the UK after Sweden issued an international arrest warrant over allegations of sexual assault.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Swedish authorities wanted to question him over claims that he had raped one woman and sexually molested and coerced another in August 2010, while on a visit to Stockholm to give a lecture. He says both encounters were entirely consensual.</span><br />\n<br />\nMr Assange was bailed in December 2010 but in May 2012 the UK's Supreme Court ruled he should be extradited to Sweden.<br />\nHe sought and was granted asylum in the Ecuadorean embassy in London. After spending almost seven years inside the embassy, he was arrested by British police on 11 April 2019. The officers removed him from the embassy's premises.<br />\n<br />\nEcuadorean President Len&iacute;n Moreno tweeted that his country had withdrawn Mr Assange's asylum status &quot;after repeated violations to international conventions and daily-life protocols&quot; in what he said was &quot;a sovereign decision&quot;."},{"pid":"e9648b08733d4b67a3c90f2f4727616b8b95d390","tid":1102003,"uid":63452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"瑞典識波，#metoo 無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04055fbcf0e6895562425a285eb55cc6dd2adfb4","tid":1102003,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Julian_Assange_20091117_Copenhagen_1_cropped_to_shoulders.jpg/250px-Julian_Assange_20091117_Copenhagen_1_cropped_to_shoulders.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F48%2FJulian_Assange_20091117_Copenhagen_1_c